<h4 id="imagine-a-windmill-that-produced-the-breeze-it-needed-to-keep-rotating-or-a-lightbulb-whose-glow-provided-its-own-electricity-these-devices-have-captured-many-inventors-imaginations-because-they-could-transform-our-relationship-with-energy" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#imagine-a-windmill-that-produced-the-breeze-it-needed-to-keep-rotating-or-a-lightbulb-whose-glow-provided-its-own-electricity-these-devices-have-captured-many-inventors-imaginations-because-they-could-transform-our-relationship-with-energy" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Imagine a windmill that produced the breeze it needed to keep rotating. Or a lightbulb whose glow provided its own electricity. These devices have captured many inventors' imaginations, because they could transform our relationship with energy.</h4>
<p>想象一下，风车制造使其不停转动的微风，电灯泡自给自足发光的电力，这些装置激发了许多发明家的想象，因为这能改变人与能源的关系。</p>
